                    <span>For the coauthor of The Courage to Heal to publish a how-to guide to reconciliation-- you just have to take off your hat in the presence of that kind of chutzpah.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">I needed her wisdom with my personal issues</div>
